实习记者 | 袁  颖编辑 | 许诗雨疫情让人们深刻了解到医疗资源的可贵。
Rain Yuan & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; Editing & # 144; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45;
某种意义上，保护医护人员和医学技术人士就是保护其他人的生命。
In a sense, protecting health-care workers and medical technologists is protecting the lives of others.
然而，医护人员的职业特殊性意味着他们在疫情中受到感染的风险更高。
However, the professional specificity of health-care workers means that they are at higher risk of infection in the context of the epidemic.
2月17日，我们第一次在公众号上用记录在这次新冠肺炎疫情中逝去医务工作者名字的方式表达敬意。
On February 17, for the first time, we paid homage to the public in the form of the names of the medical workers who died in the outbreak.
在新出版的《第一财经》杂志中，我们收录了这份名录并做了更新。
In the new issue of First Finance magazine, we have included this list and updated it.
虽然我们也曾希望这份名单再也没有更新。
Although we had hoped that the list would not be updated again.
但在那之后，又有一些医护人员离开了我们。
But after that, some paramedics left us.
同时，随着更多信息披露，更多牺牲者的名字被统计到了相关名录中。
Meanwhile, as more information came to light, more names of victims were added to the list.
因此，我们在此更新这份名单，再次用铭记致敬。
Therefore, we are here to update this list and pay tribute once again to that memory.
姜继军 51岁江苏泰州市人民医院感染科医生1月23日，姜继军医生在奔赴发热门诊时，因呼吸心跳骤停逝世。
Jiang Jijun 51-year-old Jiangsu Taizhou People's Hospital Infection Doctor January 23, Jiang Jijun rushed to the fever clinic, died of cardiac arrest due to breathing.
梁武东 62岁湖北省中西医结合医院(新华医院)耳鼻喉科原主任医师梁武东擅长显微耳神经外科、鼻内窥镜微创手术、鼾症、小儿耳鼻咽喉疾病、嗓音疾病的内外科治疗。
Liang Wudong, 62 years old, is a former chief physician in the department of otolaryngology of Hubei Province (Xinhua Hospital). Liang Wudong specializes in microsurgery, nasal endoscopic minimally invasive surgery, snoring, otorhinopharyngeal diseases and voice diseases.
鼾症喉癌功能性手术技术精湛，对分泌性中耳炎治疗方法独特，在嗓音内外科矫治领域颇有心得。
The functional operation technique of snoring laryngeal carcinoma is superb, the treatment of secretory otitis media is unique, in the field of voice surgery correction is quite knowledgeable.
1月16日，梁武东疑似感染新型冠状病毒肺炎，18日，其转到金银潭医院就诊。
January 16, Liang Wudong suspected to be infected with a new coronavirus pneumonia, 18, its transfer to the gold and silver pool hospital.
后经救治无效，梁武东于2020年1月25日早上7时许去世。
After treatment was ineffective, Liang Wudong died at about 7 a.m. on January 25, 2020.
包长命50岁内蒙古科右前旗察尔森镇沙力根嘎查村医2020年新冠肺炎疫情爆发后，他承担起全村30多名返乡人员的排查和健康检测工作。
Bao Chang-long life 50 years old Inner Mongolia Korik right front flag Charson Township Shaligan Gacha village doctor 2020 outbreak, he took over 30 village back home screening and health testing work.
1月26日，在排查检测完第14名返乡人员后，包长命突发脑出血晕倒在返回卫生室的路上，于2020年1月27日不幸离世。
On 26 January, after completing the screening and testing of the fourteenth returnee, he fainted on his way back to the health centre with a long-lived cerebral hemorrhage and died on 27 January 2020.
毛样洪52岁福建省南平市浦城县仙阳镇中心卫生院副院长1月25日晚9时许，在驻守高速检查站检测过往车辆乘员体温时被一辆轿车撞伤，后经抢救无效逝世。
Mao-like Hong 52-year-old Fujian Province Pucheng County Pu Cheng County Central Health Center Vice-Dean January 25 around 9: 00 p.m., while manning a high-speed checkpoint to check the temperature of the occupants of vehicles was injured by a car, and later died after rescue.
蒋金波58岁赣州市大余县疾控中心艾滋病防治科副科长疫情出现后，蒋金波主动请缨成为流行病学调查组的一员。
Jiang Jinbo 58 years old Ganzhou City CDC AIDS control center deputy section of the emergence of the epidemic, Jiang Jinbo volunteered to become a member of the epidemiological investigation team.
1月28日晚，蒋金波在和同事下乡指导消杀工作回到家中后，突感胸痛不适。
On the night of January 28, Jiang Jinbo and his colleagues in the countryside to guide the elimination of work back home, sudden chest pain.
在被送往大余县人民医院后，诊断考虑为心肌梗死，遂转送至赣州市人民医院。
After being sent to Dayu County People's Hospital, the diagnosis was considered as myocardial infarction and was transferred to Ganzhou People's Hospital.
终经抢救无效，于1月28日23时50分离世。
Eventually, rescue efforts failed and he was separated at 2350 hours on 28 January.
张辉56岁湖南省卫生计生综合监督局党委书记、局长张辉连续16天工作在抗疫一线，突发急性心肌梗塞，于2020年1月31日晚送医抢救无效去世。
Zhang Hui 56-year-old Hunan Health and Family Planning Bureau party secretary, director Zhang Hui 16 consecutive days of work in the frontline of the epidemic, acute myocardial infarction, on the night of January 31, 2020 sent medical emergency rescue dead.
