At about 1330 hours on January 31, 2020, Dr. Song Yunhua, a 46-year-old doctor in Taiping Community Health Room, Qinghua Street, Longyang District, Baoshan City, Yunnan Province, carried out epidemic prevention work all morning.
宋英杰28岁湖南省衡山县东湖镇马迹卫生院药剂组副组长自2020年1月25日（农历大年初一）起，宋英杰加入抗击新型冠状病毒感染肺炎疫情岳临高速东湖高速路口收费站体温检测排查团队，连续十天九夜奋斗在防控一线。
Song Yingjie 28-year-old Hunan Hengshan County Donghu Town Ma Tian Hospital Pharmacy Group since January 25, 2020 (Lunar New Year's Day), Song Yingjie joined the fight against the new coronavirus infection pneumonia epidemic Yue in the high-speed East Lake toll booth temperature screening team, 10 consecutive days and nights struggle in the prevention and control front.
2月3日零点值班结束交接完班后回到宿舍，因过度劳累引发心源性猝死。
February 3 duty at the end of the handover after returning to the dormitory, due to excessive fatigue caused sudden cardiac death.
姚留记68岁河南省平顶山市郏县冢头镇北街村党支部委员、卫生室医生2020年2月4日13时9分，姚留记突然昏倒在执勤岗位上，后经抢救无效不幸去世。
Yao Liuzhi 68 years old No Jiaxian No No Xian No No Xian Xian No. North Street Village, Henan Province On February 4, 2020 at 13: 09, Yao Liuji suddenly fainted on duty and died after unsuccessful rescue.
张建华49岁陕西咸阳市旬邑县湫坡头镇卫生院公共卫生科职工新冠肺炎疫情来袭时，张建华第一时间在全镇开展疫情知识宣传，落实防护措施。
Zhang Jianhua 49 years old Shanxi Xianyang Xunyi Xunyi town health center public health department staff new crown pneumonia outbreak, Zhang Jianhua the first time in the town to carry out epidemic knowledge dissemination, implementation of protective measures.
他联合18名乡村医生，对镇上的外来人口及存在风险做排查，及时掌握40多名湖北返乡人员的情况，上报县卫健部门。
Together with 18 village doctors, he screened the town's migrant population and the risks involved, promptly grasped the situation of more than 40 Hubei returnees and reported it to the county health department.
2020年2月5日，在新冠肺炎防控工作中，张建华因心脏病抢救无效去世。
On February 5, 2020, Zhang Jianhua died of a heart attack during the prevention and control of New Crown Pneumonia.
