Xiao Jun, 40-year-old Wuhan Red Cross Hospital (also known as the Wuhan Red Cross Hospital) General Surgeon Xiao Jun was admitted to Wuhan Red Cross Hospital on January 26, 2020. He was admitted to Wuhan Red Cross Hospital on January 27, 2020.
