2月9日，指挥部安排他第一次轮休。
On 9 February, the headquarters arranged his first rotation.
由于疲惫，张军浩睡到下午3点才起床，妻子张柳准备午餐时，发现他倒在客厅地上。
Because of exhaustion, Zhang Junhao did not get up until 3 pm. When his wife, Zhang Liu, prepared lunch, she found him lying on the floor of the living room.
等120救护车赶到，他心跳已停止。
By the time 120 ambulances arrived, his heart had stopped.
2020年2月9日，张军浩因突发心肌梗塞抢救无效去世。
