Mr. Wang goes to the quarantined person's home twice a day to take his temperature and instruct them to disinfect their homes.
此外，王土成还积极宣传疫情防控知识，每天在村里的微信群里讲解什么是新冠肺炎、传播途径以及怎样预防等，增加了村民应对疫情的信心。
In addition, Wang Tucheng actively publicized the disease prevention and control knowledge, daily in the village micro-letter group to explain what is the new crown pneumonia, how to spread and how to prevent, and so on, increased villagers' confidence in dealing with the epidemic.
