许德甫62岁中医主任医师、鄂州名医、湖北中医药大学兼职教授、北京中医药大学付延龄医学研究中心研究员、湖北省中医中药学会脾胃病专业委员会常务委员、鄂州市中医中药学会常务理事。
Xu Defu, 62, chief physician of TCM, an adjunct professor at Hubei University of Traditional Chinese Medicine, a researcher at Fu Longying Medical Research Center of Beijing TCM University, Standing Committee Member of Spleen and Gastric Disease Committee of Hubei Traditional Chinese Medicine Society, and Managing Director of Huzhou Traditional Chinese Medicine Society.
在长期临床实践中，逐步摸索了一套临床经验，形成自身的医疗特色，临床用药灵活，以廉、简、便、验见长，对疑难杂症的诊治颇有心得，特别是对肝胆脾胃病的诊治有独到之处，对胃病、消化道、糖尿病等疾病的治疗亦经验丰富。
In the long-term clinical practice, gradually grope for a set of clinical experience, form their own medical characteristics, clinical drug use flexibility, to save money, simple, convenient, long-term experience, the diagnosis and treatment of difficult diseases, especially the liver, gallbladder, stomach disease, treatment of stomach, digestive tract, diabetes and other diseases has unique experience.
发表学术论文50余篇，出版《中西药不合理联用150例》、《中西医结合治疗常见肿瘤的良方妙法》等专著8部。
More than 50 academic papers have been published, including 150 cases of unreasonable use of Chinese and Western medicine, and 8 monographs on the combination of traditional Chinese and Western medicine in the treatment of common cancers.
2020年2月13日，许德甫因感染新型冠状病毒肺炎去世。
On February 13, 2020, Xu Defu died of pneumonia, a new coronavirus.
刘筱娴 83岁华中科技大学同济医学院公共卫生学院教授、研究生导师、中华预防医学会社会医学学会常务理事、儿童保健学会常务理事、湖北妇幼保健管理学会副理事长、湖北省性学会副理事长、中国疾病预防控制中心妇幼保健中心顾问委员会委员、湖北省儿童全面发展研究会理事长、中华预防医学会武汉妇幼保健学会主任委员、华中科技大学同济医学院伤害控制研究中心荣誉主任、学术委员会主任委员。
Professor, Graduate Tutor, School of Public Health, Tongji School of Medicine, CUHK; Executive Director, Chinese Society of Preventive Medicine; Vice-President, Hubei Institute of Maternal and Child Health; Vice-President, Hubei Institute of Maternal and Child Health; Chairman, Wuhan Society of Preventive Medicine; Honorary Director, Injury Control Research Center, Tongji Medical School, CUHK; Chairman, Academic Council.
刘筱娴是我国高等教育妇幼卫生专业创建者。
Liu Xiaoxian is the founder of maternal and child health specialty in higher education.
为培养妇幼专业人才，她于1985年创办我国第一个本科妇幼卫生专业，为国家培养了一大批妇幼保健专业人才并成为我国妇幼卫生事业的中坚力量。
To train professional women and children, in 1985 she founded China's first undergraduate course in maternal and child health care, trained a large number of women and children professionals and became the backbone of China's maternal and child health cause.
刘筱娴还是国家农村基层保健网的建设者。
Liu Xiaoxian is also the national rural grass-roots health network builders.
在1970 年代，她选定革命老区麻城县为基地，以报出生、报死亡、报传染病、报肿瘤发病(“四报”) 为主要内容建立了农村基层三级妇幼保健网。
In the 1970s, she selected the old revolutionary district of Massachusetts as a base to report births, deaths, reported infectious diseases and reported tumours ("four newspapers") as the main content to establish a rural grass-roots three-level maternal and child health care network.
她在20年间培养了大批乡村医生，她的工作也使得麻城县被联合国儿童基金会列入全国第一批妇幼卫生示范县。
She trained a large number of village doctors in 20 years, and her work led to her being listed by UNICEF as one of the first maternal and child health model counties in the country.
2月13日，刘筱娴因医治无效在武汉同济医院逝世。
February 13, Liu Xiaoxian invalid medical treatment in Wuhan Tongji Hospital died.
柳帆59岁武汉武昌医院梨园街社区卫生院服务中心注射室护士2月15日，武汉武昌医院发布消息称，因年资较长，柳帆没有被安排去发热门诊导医台，预检分诊台等一线工作，始终在社区从事注射工作。
Liu Fan 59-year-old Wuhan Wuchang Hospital Li Yuen Street Community Health Center Injection Room Nurse, Wuhan Wuchang Hospital said Feb. 15, because of the long experience, willow sail has not been arranged to heat out-patient clinic, pre-check-up clinic and other frontline work, always doing injection work in the community.
据悉，柳帆在生前主动申请了延迟退休。
It is reported that Liufan in his own initiative to apply for delayed retirement.
2月14日17：30左右，柳帆出现心脏骤停，后于18：30左右因抢救无效去世。
February 14 around 17: 30, willow sail suddenly stopped heart, and then around 18: 30 because rescue failed to die.
陈祥田36岁江西省芦溪县银河镇长竹村长布卫生计生服务室乡村医生1月27日下午，陈祥田因劳累过度诱发疾病被紧急送往医院检查抢救，诊断为急性髓系白血病，经全力救治无效于2020年2月14日中午去世。
Chen Xiangtian 36-year-old Jiangxi Luxi County Yinhe Village Chief Bamboo Health and Family Service Room Village Doctor Chen Xiangtian was rushed to hospital on the afternoon of January 27 because of excessive fatigue caused by illness, diagnosis of acute myeloid leukemia, after full treatment futile died on February 14, 2020.
段正澄 86岁中国工程院院士、华中科技大学机械科学与工程学院教授、制造装备数字化国家工程研究中心首席科学家、机械制造与自动化专家1996年，段正澄将机械科学与放疗医学相结合，研发了国际首台全身伽马刀。
Duan Zhengcheng 86-year-old academician of the Chinese Academy of Engineering, Professor of Mechanical Sciences and Engineering of Huazhong University of Science and Technology, Chief Scientist of the National Engineering Research Center for Digitalization of Manufacturing Equipment and Expert in Mechanical Manufacturing and Automation.
1999年，段正澄研发的世界首台大型放疗设备——全身伽马刀问世，全身伽马刀可进行旋转动态聚焦，使伽马射线焦点对准经过精密定位后的肿瘤，从而杀死肿瘤细胞，大大降低对人体正常组织和器官的损伤。
In 1999, Danzheng Cheng-cheng developed the world's first large-scale radiotherapy device, the gamma knife, which rotates and focuses gamma rays on precisely located tumors, killing tumor cells and greatly reducing damage to normal tissues and organs.
目前已在全国100多家医院使用，惠及近百万人。
It is now in use in more than 100 hospitals throughout the country, benefiting nearly 1 million people.
段正澄教授于1月29日确诊了新型冠状病毒肺炎，其本身患有糖尿病等基础疾病，最终因医治无效，于2月15日19时35分在医院逝世。
Professor Duan Zhengcheng confirmed the case of a new coronavirus pneumonia on January 29. He suffered from basic diseases such as diabetes and died at 19: 35 on February 15 due to ineffective medical treatment.
左汉文湖北省广水市太平镇群联村卫生所医生左汉文在新冠肺炎疫情防控工作中，突发心脏病，于2020年2月15日不幸逝世。
Left Hanwen, a doctor at Liancun Health Center, Taiping Town Group, Guangshui City, Hubei Province, died on February 15, 2020 after suffering a heart attack during the prevention and control of pneumonia.
刘智明51岁武汉武昌医院院长，湖北中医药大学和江汉大学硕士研究生导师刘智明1991年毕业于武汉大学医学院，擅长颅脑外伤、颅内肿瘤、脑血管病及椎管内病的诊断和治疗，特别擅长神经外科疾病手术治疗。
Liu Zhiming, 51, director of Wuhan Wuchang Hospital, Hubei University of Chinese Medicine, and Liu Zhiming, a master's degree supervisor from Jianghan University, graduated from Wuhan University School of Medicine in 1991. He specializes in the diagnosis and treatment of craniocerebral trauma, intracranial tumors, cerebrovascular diseases and intravertebral diseases.
刘智明2013年曾被武昌区委区政府授予“武昌英才”荣誉称号、2014年获“武汉市人民政府博士资助”人选、2015年获武汉市“十百千人才工程”人选。
In 2013, Liu Zhiming was awarded the honorary title of "Wuchang Talent" by the regional government of Wuchang District, a candidate for PhD funding from Wuhan Municipal People's Government in 2014, and a candidate for the "Ten Thousand Talent Project" in Wuhan City in 2015.
直至确诊前，刘智明始终工作在抗疫第一线。
Until the diagnosis, Liu Zhiming has been working in the first line of the epidemic.
1月23日，接收完病人的刘智明表示自己身体不舒服，当时刘智明已经连续多日发热，24日检查的CT结果显示，肺部感染严重，刘智明很快被收进了ICU。
After receiving the patient on January 23, Liu said he was unwell, having been feverish for days, and CT findings on the 24th showed a severe lung infection and Liu was admitted to the ICU.
1月28日，核酸确诊阳性。
On 28 January, nucleic acid was confirmed positive.
2月18日上午10:30，刘智明因感染新冠肺炎抢救无效逝世。
Feb. 18, 10: 30 am, Liu Zhiming died of pneumonia due to infection.
王兵73岁武汉市洪山区王兵西医内科诊所主治医师因在新冠肺炎疫情防控期间感染新冠肺炎，王兵于2020年2月18日不幸逝世。
Wang Bing 73-year-old Wuhan Hongshan Wang Bing Western Medicine Clinic doctor for the new crown pneumonia during the prevention and control of the new crown pneumonia, Wang Bing died on February 18, 2020.
彭银华29岁武汉市江夏区第一人民医院/协和江南医院呼吸与危重症医学科医生据江夏融媒1月28日报道，彭银华医生本打算正月初八举办婚礼，但因疫情来袭，他延迟婚期上一线，办公桌抽屉里还放着没来得及分发的请柬。
Dr. Peng Yinhua, 29, was planning to hold his wedding on January 8, but because of the outbreak of the disease, he delayed his wedding and had an invitation card in his desk drawer that had not been distributed.
“疫情不散，婚期延迟”，也是彭银华和妻子达成的共识。
"The epidemic is not over, marriage is delayed," Peng Yinhua and his wife reached a consensus.
1月25日，彭银华感染新冠肺炎后入住江夏区第一人民医院接受救治；1月30日因病情加重，医院紧急将其送往武汉市金银潭医院治疗。
On January 25, Peng Yinhua was admitted to Jiangxia First People's Hospital for treatment after contracting pneumonia.
2月20日21时50分，因病情恶化，经抢救无效，彭银华在武汉市金银潭医院去世。
At 2150 hours on February 20, Peng Yinhua died at the Gold and Silver Pool Hospital in Wuhan after failing to rescue him.
吴忠泽50岁武汉天安医院体检部主任吴忠泽医生连续半个月奋斗在新冠肺炎疫情防控一线，因突发脑溢血于2020年2月20日抢救无效去世。
Wu Zhongze 50-year-old Wuhan Tianan Hospital Medical Director Wu Zhongze for half a month in the first line of prevention and control of the new crown pneumonia, due to sudden cerebral haemorrhage on February 20, 2020 rescue died.
夏思思29岁武汉协和江北医院消化内科住院医师夏思思在救治患者过程中不幸感染新冠肺炎，1月19日，她突然发起高烧，经检查发现肺部CT磨玻璃影改变，高度疑似，随后在武汉协和江北医院隔离治疗。
Xiaxis, 29, Wuhan Concorde Jiangbei Hospital Digestive Medicine resident Xiaxis in the treatment of patients with pneumonia, January 19, she suddenly launched a high fever, examination found that the lung CT grinding glass shadow, highly suspected, and then in Wuhan Concorde Jiangbei hospital for treatment.
2月7日半夜，夏思思病情突然加重，呼吸、心跳骤停，医院连夜组织抢救，保住了生命，但一直处于昏迷状态，血氧饱和度很低，在上了ECMO（人工心肺）后立马转至武汉大学中南医院。
February 7 midnight, Xia Si suddenly aggravated illness, breathing, cardiac arrest, the hospital overnight organization rescue, saved life, but has been in a coma, blood oxygen saturation is very low, immediately after ECMO (artificial cardiopulmonary) transfer to Wuhan University Zhongnan Hospital.
在ICU夏思思病情血压波动大，于2月23日凌晨6:30分，抢救无效离世。
In ICU summer sickness blood pressure fluctuation, February 23 at 6: 30 a.m., rescue failed to die.
杜显圣55岁海南省琼中黎族自治县阳江医院医生1月22日杜显圣到儋州市人民医院就诊，医院怀疑其被新型冠状病毒感染，1月24日采样送检，1月25日新型冠状病毒核酸检测阳性，被确诊为新型冠状病毒肺炎，随即由儋州市人民医院转到海南省人民医院。
Du Xiangsheng 55-year-old Henan Province Qiongzhong Li County Yangjiang Hospital doctor January 22 Danzhou People's Hospital Danzhou City Hospital, suspected of being infected with the new coronavirus, January 24 sample sent for inspection, January 25, a new coronavirus positive, confirmed as a new coronavirus pneumonia, immediately transferred from Danzhou People's Hospital to Hainan Province People's Hospital.
杜显圣1月26日病情恶化告病危，此后，省人民医院每天组织两次病历讨论，并请院外远程会诊14次，包括王辰院士、李兰娟院士、广州呼吸病研究所黎毅敏教授，指挥部省级专家组组织会诊6次；组织救治70余次，其中重大抢救9次；70余名医务人员参与治疗和抢救，采取了呼吸机辅助治疗、气管切开、人工膜肺（ECMO）支持心肺功能、输入康复者血浆等各种救治措施。
Since then, the Provincial People's Hospital has organized two daily medical records discussions and 14 consultation sessions with people outside the hospital, including Academician Wang Chen, Academician Li Lanjuan and Professor Li Yi-min of Guangzhou Respiratory Disease Research Institute.
但由于其病情恶化，抢救无效，于2月23日12：36心跳骤停，13：50确认死亡。
However, due to the deterioration of his condition, rescue efforts failed, on 23 February at 12: 36 cardiac arrest, 13: 50 confirmed death.
黄文军42岁孝感市中心医院呼吸内科副主任医师黄文军在抗击新型冠状病毒肺炎的战役中不幸被感染，经多方抢救医治无效，于2020年2月23日下午19时30分，不幸牺牲。
Huang Wenjun 42-year-old filial piety city hospital deputy director of respiratory medicine physician Huang Wenjun in the battle against the new coronavirus pneumonia unfortunately infected, after multi-rescue medical treatment failed, 23 February 2020 at 1930 hours, unfortunately died.
崔靖56岁湖北省京山市卫生健康局党组成员崔靖在新冠肺炎疫情防控工作期间，突发急性肾功能衰竭，于2020年2月24日经抢救无效因公殉职。
Cui Jing, 56, a member of the Party Group of the Jingshan Health Bureau of Hubei Province, died in the line of duty on February 24, 2020 after suffering acute renal failure during the prevention and control of the new crown pneumonia epidemic.
江学庆55岁武汉市中心医院甲状腺乳腺外科党支部书记、主任、主任医师江学庆医生在抗击新冠肺炎疫情工作中不幸染病，经全力抢救无效，于2020年3月1日凌晨5点32分在武汉市肺科医院去世。
Jiang Xueqing 55-year-old Wuhan Central Hospital Thyroid Breast Surgery Branch Secretary, Director and Chief Physician Dr. Jiang Xueqing died on March 1, 2020 at 5: 32 a.m. in Wuhan City Lung Hospital after failing to do his utmost to save him.
梅仲明57岁武汉市中心医院眼科副主任、主任医师据公开资料显示，梅仲明擅长青光眼、白内障、眼后段等疾病的诊断、治疗，曾荣获武汉市“光明特使”称号。
Mei Zhongming 57-year-old Wuhan City Central Hospital, deputy director of ophthalmology, director of the doctor, according to open data showed that Mezhongming good at glaucoma, cataract, posterior segment of the eye, and has been named "special envoy of light" in Wuhan.
梅仲明在抗击新冠肺炎疫情工作中不幸感染新冠肺炎，经全力抢救无效，于2020年3月3日中午12时在武汉市金银潭医院去世。
On March 3, 2020, Mei Zhongming died at 12: 00 noon in Wuhan city after failing to save his newly infected crown pneumonia.
朱和平69岁武汉市中心医院眼科副主任医师朱和平医生退休后被医院返聘，担任武汉市中心医院眼科副主任医师，擅长眼底病诊断治疗，眼前后节激光治疗。
Zhu Heping, 69, deputy director of ophthalmology at Wuhan Central Hospital, was rehired by the hospital after his retirement as deputy chief ophthalmologist at Wuhan Central Hospital.
朱和平医生于2月中旬入院治疗，3月9日上午抢救无效，不幸离世。
Dr. Zhu was admitted to hospital in mid-February and died on the morning of 9 March after failing to rescue him.
至此，武汉市中心医院在抗疫中已有四位医生因感染新冠肺炎不幸去世。
So far, Wuhan city central hospital in the fight against the disease has four doctors died of pneumonia due to the new crown.
此外，在国家卫建委3月5日发布的“全国卫生健康系统新冠肺炎疫情防控工作先进个人名单”中，还收录了以下几位我们尚未获得完整身份信息的医务工作者：邓林  年龄不详，武汉急救中心科员病因、逝世时间不详阮惠芳 年龄不详，湖北省长江航运总医院技师病因、逝世时间不详张抗美 年龄不详，武汉市硚口区宝丰街社区卫生服务中心医师病因、逝世时间不详陈清山年龄不详，荆门市京山仁和医院主治医师病因、逝世时间不详周宗德 年龄不详，武汉科技大学附属天佑医院技术工三级病因、逝世时间不详2月16日，全国第1、第2例新冠肺炎逝世患者的遗体解剖工作在武汉金银潭医院完成，并成功拿到新冠肺炎病理。
In addition, the state health committee on March 5 released the "National Health Health System New Crown Pneumonia advanced personnel list", we also included the following medical workers: unknown age, Wuhan Emergency and Emergency Center staff etiology, death time unknown, Wuhan Changjiang Hospital Medical Center, unknown etiology, death time unknown, Wuhan City Zengkou District Po Fung Street Hospital Medical Doctor etiology and death of unknown age,
由解剖获得的新冠肺炎病理，对于探索新冠肺炎患者临床的病理改变，疾病机制等有重大帮助，并能从根本上寻找新冠肺炎的致病性，致死性，给未来临床治疗危重症患者提供依据。
The pathology of new crown pneumonia obtained from anatomy is of great help in exploring the pathologic changes and disease mechanism of patients with new crown pneumonia, and can fundamentally find out the pathogenicity and fatal nature of the new crown pneumonia, and provide evidence for future clinical treatment of critically ill patients.
我们同样向这两位捐献者及家属致敬。
We also pay tribute to the two donors and their families.
